channel.title: How weird is this?
channel.description:
Ok so ive known this guy for like 2 years on msn. And i got talking to him now and he said he is a member of the Artic Monkeys. Of course i didnt beleive him but he went on webcam and its actually them!! so ive known him all this time and not known hes in a famous band.
Anyhow hes getting me free tickets!!!
How weird is that?
